DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

01-282. In re Bailey.

Upon consideration of movant’s amended motion to suppress deposition and movant’s motion to compel Columbus Bar Association to provide names, business location, or address of unauthorized practice of law committee,

*1480IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motions be, and hereby are, denied.

Lundberg Stratton, J., would grant the motion to compel.
